<L>__{interior mackelway's apartment bedroom resuming}
<A>__{mackelway stares out the window; seems like he just heard that scream. of course, that'd be impossible. he looks to that map. his phone rings. he eyes it, unsurprised...}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{exterior woods outside sleeper, mo. later}
<A>__{law enforcement vehicles surround the site. cops, grieves, coroner's guys taking pictures. loretta is sitting on the back of an ambulance, being tended to. a composite artist sits beside her, trying.}
