<D>__{narrower?}
<C>__{loretta}
<D>__{no, they were... i don't really know.}
<A>__{composite artist keeps trying, but his attempt doesn't look anything like the face of o'ryan. charlton, meanwhile, stands over the body, mind racing. a missouri highway patrol car pulls up. mackelway steps out of it. we follow him as he takes in the scene. a flashbulb illuminates starkey's chest; is got a zero with a slash through it. but mackelway hasn't seen the guy's face yet.}
<C>__{mackelway}
<D>__{sir?}
