<D>__{no. starkey's the one on the ground.}
<A>__{mackelway pauses, thinks he must've heard wrong. but he turns toward the face, as another flashbulb illuminates it, searing the image into the darkness. starkey. dead. his eyelids ripped away. mackelway stares, stunned. can't fucking believe it.}
